<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ur" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>درخواست برائے منتقلی پلاٹ - رسید</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Nastaliq+Urdu:wght@400;700&display=swap');
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Nastaliq Urdu', serif;
            direction: rtl;
            text-align: right;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2c5aa0;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header h2 {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        
        .receipt-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .receipt-info h3 {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #ccc;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #495057;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            color: #212529;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .application-details {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .application-details h3 {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .attachments-list {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .attachments-list h4 {
            color: #495057;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .attachment-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 5px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #ccc;
        }
        
        .attachment-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .qr-code {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .status-submitted {
            background: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
        }
        
        .status-under-scrutiny {
            background: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
        }
        
        @media print {
            body {
                padding: 0;
            }
            
            .header, .receipt-info, .application-details, .footer {
                break-inside: avoid;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>محکمہ ہاؤسنگ</h1>
        <h2>درخواست برائے منتقلی پلاٹ - رسید</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="receipt-info">
        <h3>رسید کی تفصیلات</h3>
        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">رسید نمبر:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{application.id}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">تاریخ:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{formatDate application.createdAt}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">وقت:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{formatTime application.createdAt}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">حالت:</span>
                <span class="info-value">
                    <span class="status-badge status-{{application.currentStage}}">
                        {{getStatusText application.currentStage}}
                    </span>
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="application-details">
        <h3>درخواست کی تفصیلات</h3>
        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">درخواست کنندہ:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{application.applicantName}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">فون نمبر:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{application.applicantPhone}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">پلاٹ نمبر:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{plot.plotNumber}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">بلاک:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{plot.block}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">سکشن:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{plot.section}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-label">سائز:</span>
                <span class="info-value">{{plot.size}} مرلہ</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        {{#if attachments}}
        <div class="attachments-list">
            <h4>منسلک دستاویزات</h4>
            {{#each attachments}}
            <div class="attachment-item">
                <span>{{getDocTypeText this.docType}}</span>
                <span>{{#if this.originalSeen}}✓ اصلی دیکھا گیا{{else}}✗ اصلی نہیں دیکھا{{/if}}</span>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>
        {{/if}}
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>یہ رسید درخواست کی وصولی کی تصدیق کرتی ہے</p>
        <p>برائے مزید معلومات: {{application.id}}</p>
        <div class="qr-code">
            {{#if qrCodeDataURL}}
            <img src="{{qrCodeDataURL}}" alt="QR Code" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain;">
            {{else}}
            QR Code<br>
            {{application.id}}
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
